title.rendered: STEDI DUAL USB 4X4 VOLT METER GAUGE MONITOR

content.rendered:
Dual Display 4×4 Volt Gauge Monitor

 

 

DETAILS

Dual USB with built in Volt Gauge Monitor.

  • Blue LED Displays
  • Fits the same cut outs as our Carling type rocker switches
  • Display Range 0 to 28 Volts
  • Flush mounted
  • Water-resistant
  • Cut-out hole size: 37.2 x 21.2mm
  • 2.1A each output

SPECIFICATIONS

.

VOLTAGE 12v & 24v
OUTPUT DC 5V 2.1A / 2.1A
MATERIAL ABS

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 1x DUAL USB CHARGER / VOLT GAUGE
